summary: Chasing the Dreams
title: Chasing the Dreams
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2PooVv9

by ordinaryrunaway

He thought about the boy in the red coat, who wore sorrow like a second skin, who smelled of rain, earth and mystery. That boy made his skin prickle with excitement. There was an air of familiarity surrounding him, even though Loki was sure that he had never seen that boy in his life before.
-
“So, you don’t remember me then.” His voice was quiet, broken, and Loki just gave up. This was too much.
